title: PAR_map Plant Adapation Regions
name: PAR_map Plant Adapation Regions
description: The plant adaptation region map (PAR) is a combination of Bailey's ecoregion map at the province level and the US major hardiness zone map.  Ecoregions and hardiness zone classification systems integrate many climate and geographic variables that determine plant adaptation, they can be combined to develop PAR's.
